# To perform input and output operation

## we nned to import java.io

1. Byte Stream - can read and write data in bytes(8 bits).
2. Char Stream - this can read and write in data data 2 bytes (16 bits).

## when we are working with text data char stream is prefrred otherwise Byte Strem.

## to improve the io operation(read and write) Buffering is used.

### there is also the bridge classes.

## Reading the values in java

1. Through keyboard using Scanner sc.
2. Buffer Reader br using bridge.

